Introduction

NINE.i is an eight-member boy group under FirstOne Entertainment. They were first introduced through a conceptual project called "The Birth of a New Algorithm." They made their official debut as ten on March 30, 2022, with the mini album "New World."

On January 28, 2024, FirstOne announced that Winnie had left the group due to his shoulder injury.

On March 15, the members, excluding Eden, shared that they are currently in a legal dispute against FirstOne. Later on June 12, it was announced that matters with FirstOne has been resolved and the group would be preparing for a new start and discussing the direction of future activities.

On March 11, 2025, it was announced that Joohyoung had decided to part ways with the group.
